leads.lead_text: Anther cone slightly exserted from corolla-tube; filaments bent but not twisted; fruit more or less terete; widespread plant of wet forests
Anther cone long-exserted above the corolla; filaments spirally twisted; fruit narrow-ovoid; rare plant from rock outcrops along the upper Snowy River
